Went to Katie's it was fun saw Soli for the first time in a long time. It was nice...i guess but yea I dont know anymore....

Today i went to the Movies with Cameron and Morgan. It was fun I always have fun with them. I only wish we hung out more thow...but yea..It was really fun we say Peter Pan I loved it Morgan thought it was "Alright" Cameron hated it and thought it was dumb but i really liked it. If i were you i would go and see it...its so worth your time......
